---

##Lessons Learned

- Planning and implementing `/25` subnetting
- Router configuration for multi-LAN communication
- Enforcing Layer-2 access control with sticky MAC security
- Converting a consumer router to AP mode & disabling DHCP
- Documenting network design and addressing tables clearly

---

##Next Improvements

- Add VLANs + trunking instead of physical segmentation
- Implement ACLs to restrict traffic between LANs
- Add DHCP server for automated address assignment
- Introduce firewall or pfSense for perimeter security

